	<presentation id="index">
		<title short="How hard can it be?">How hard can it be? The case for API Platforms</title>
		<toc class="abstract">Platform engineering is a popular topic, and for very good reasons. With the growing number of available digital building blocks and the growing number of the new ones we're building, scaling the practice of how to best do that becomes important. We look into what platform engineering is all about, how it compares to API management and API platforms, and what the API space can do to help platform engineering initiatives. We also look at a popular platform engineering maturity model and how it can help you to better navigate the API platform space.</toc>
